snippet.title: How Could She - Johnny Depp is Angry Amber Heard Hasn't Paid The Donation!
snippet.description:
"How Could She?" - Johnny Depp is Angry Amber Heard Hasn't Paid The Donation!

In this video, we are taking a look at the Amber Heard / Johnny Depp Divorce settlement news.  This divorce has been all over the media the last year, social media had a lot to play on the verdict.  Well, not Johnny is mad because all sources are showing that Amber Heard did not pay the $7Million to charities like she promised.  Even women's rights groups have stopped supporting her at this point.  Watch until the end to learn all about it.

Don't forget to subscribe for all of our updates.
